Key Match Events: Hakim Ziyech scored the only goal of the match for Morocco
Post-Match Reflections: Morocco's win allowed Ivory Coast to qualify for the last 16
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was only the third time Morocco and Zambia have met in the Africa Cup of Nations
Others: Morocco coach Walid Regragui was banned for two matches following a post-match clash with DR Congo captain Chancel Mbemba on Sunday
